data.description: Price reduction! Don't miss this opportunity. Move right into your corner-lot home with stunning mountain and city views, where sleek modern vibes meet natural charm. The airy layout is perfect for hosting gatherings or just kicking back. Bask in the natural sunlight pouring through the tall, floor to ceiling windows and skylights that brings the outdoor nature in. Conveniently located, getting in and out is a breeze.  The carport fits two cars and has a direct entrance right into the houseyou'll stay dry on rainy daysInside, you'll find a spacious great room, complete with a cozy fireplace. There is a welcoming, open floor plan with high ceilings and tasteful beams, adding an architectural touch. The kitchen and laundry areas are practical for day to day living. The three bedrooms are all good sizes.Take in the sweeping hillside vistas from indoors, blending indoor comfort with outdoor beauty. Plus, there may be potential to expand another story below the main house to suit your needs.The lot has a variety of trees and plants. The landscaping can be cut back to your taste, creating more outdoor living area. Whether you're ready to move right in or eager to put your stamp on things, this home fits your lifestyle.This property is a rare find, offering not just a stylish home but a canvas for your unique vision. Don't let this opportunity slip by. Make this exceptional residence yours today!
